    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1880-08-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1880-08-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="622" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d622">
                <head>No. 622.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Evarts</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Heap</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1880-08-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 23,
                                1880</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Urge upon government prompt and condign punishment of the murderers, and
                            energetic measures to protect other American missionaries and citizens
                            in the disturbed region.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>EVARTS, <hi rend="italic">Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
